  * Bump standards version to 3.9.8
  * Fix typo in filter_api.c, 06_filter_api_typo.diff

  [ Jonas Maurus ]
  * Fix segfault in table_postgres if connections suddenly close and
    PQresultErrorField returns NULL. 05_TABLE_POSTGRES.diff

